    3.0    Installation from a release diskette

    Use this procedure if you received your software on a release
    diskette. If you downloaded a .ZIP file from our support system refer
    to section 3.2 and 3.3.

    Copying files from install diskette to your system.
    ---------------------------------------------------

    In order to install the software place the release diskette in your
    floppy diskette drive and type the following command;

    A: 
    INSTALL A: C:\BBSV6

    Note: If your floppy diskette is B: then substitute "B:" for "A:"
    above. Also, if you would like it installed on another drive or in 
    another directory, please substitute your drive and directory for the 
    "C:\BBSV6" above.

    The install procedure will copy the appropriate files to BBSV6
    directory with sample databases ready to generate starmaps on.




    3.1   Upgrade from a release diskette

    Use this procedure if you received a software update on a
    release diskette. If you downloaded a .ZIP file from our support
    system refer to section 3.2 and 3.3.

    NOTE: ALWAYS BACKUP YOUR SYSTEM PRIOR TO MAKING ANY 
    MAJOR CHANGES! 

    STEP 1:   
    Copying files from install diskette to your system.

    In order to update the software place the release diskette in your
    floppy diskette drive and type the following command;

    A: 
    UPDATE A: C:\BBSV6

    Note: If your floppy diskette is B: then substitute "B:" for "A:"
    above. Also, if you would like it installed on another drive or in 
    another directory, please substitute your drive and directory for the 
    "C:\BBSV6" above.

    The update procedure will copy the appropriate files to your BBS
    directory but will not effect your existing databases.




    3.2   Installation from a downloaded ZIP file.

    Use this procedure if you received your first copy of the software
    by downloading it from our support BBS. If you are updating a
    previous release please refer to section 3.3 below.

    STEP 1:   
    
    Copy the downloaded file to your BBSV6 directory

    COPY MBMGEMAP.ZIP C:\BBSV6

    Note: If you would like it installed on another drive or in 
    another directory, please substitute your drive and directory for the 
    "C:" and "\BBSV6" above.

    STEP 2:

    Switch to the BBSV6 Directory

    C:
    CD \BBSV6

    Note: If you would like it installed on another drive or in 
    another directory, please substitute your drive and directory for the 
    "C:" and "\BBSV6" above.

    STEP 4:   
    Unzipping the downloaded file.

    PKUNZIP MBMGEMAP.ZIP




